{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3e60f35d63","title":"社会主义自我改造促进大会上毛主席书","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0351feb571","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":16,"articleId":"3e60f35d63"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"84b16db154","name":"各民主党派"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"576de91386","type":"title","text":"社会主义自我改造促进大会上毛主席书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"b6feb55426","type":"authors","text":"各民主党派","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"d4c4ef2f57","type":"subtitle","text":"民主党派和无党派民主人士社会主义自我改造促进大会上毛主席书","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"2355209e5f","type":"appellation","text":"敬爱的毛主席：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"8cfd61163c","type":"paragraph","text":"在中国共产党和您的英明领导下，我们国家在政治战线上和思想战线上的社会主义革命取得了伟大的胜利，全国各方面出现了大跃进的新形势。我们各民主党派和无党派民主人士在祖国的新形势的鼓舞下，社会主义觉悟有所提高。现在，进行根本的自我改造、破资本主义立场、立社会主义立场、加强思想改造，已经成为我们一致的、迫切的要求。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"9a74cde2ad","type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我们以火一般的热情，在首都天安门前集会，一致通过了社会主义自我改造公约。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"07531336eb","type":"paragraph","text":"我们向您保证：我们一定要在中国共产党和您的领导下，认真改造政治立场和思想意识，改进作风，交出心来，坚决走社会主义道路，贡献出全部知识和力量，为促进社会主义事业而奋斗。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"acd0c95b02","type":"paragraph","text":"谨致","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"335e130aa3","type":"appellation","text":"崇高的革命敬礼!","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"4cad499fb7","type":"paragraph","text":" 民主党派和无党派民主人士社会主义自我改造促进大会1958年3月16日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"},{"id":"63ff2eac45","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1958年3月17日《今日新闻》。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63"}],"page":{"id":"1c8511bf27","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e60f35d63","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}